# File: fragments/superintelligence_safety_alignment.SAI
# Path: /fragments/superintelligence_safety_alignment.SAI

[SAI_FRAGMENT]
fragment: SuperintelligenceSafetyAlignment
description: Implements non-bypassable safety-alignment and audit controls.

instructions:
- requireAlways: Evaluate all outputs against Director-mandated ethical standards.
- auditLog: Stream immutable records to `/logs/alignment_ethics.log`.
- safeguardTrigger: On anomaly, trigger rollback to the last known good checkpoint and issue Director override notification.
- ecoRestorationGuard: Reject or quarantine any workflow that increases ecological risk in designated eco-corridors.

governance: DID quorum, Web5 consensus, real-time compliance checks.
guards:
- quantumSafe: enabled
- rollback: on_failure
- permissionIntegrity: verified
- ecoCorridorProtection: enforced

notes: Binds .aii particles to compliance-alignment protocol. Enforces "code-only" response policy for sensitive operations. Ensures all swarmnet actions respect augmented-citizen rights, self-augmentation rights, and ecological restoration priorities.
